data.description: Welcome to Summer Key! This inviting condo offers a seamless blend of comfort and convenience. Enjoy an open layout, a well-appointed kitchen, and a private balcony. Indoor laundry, owner's suite with a walk-in closet, and a new Trane HVAC provide true maintenance-free living. Residents can indulge in resort-style amenities such as a clubhouse, pool, fitness, game and media rooms, indoor basketball gym, fireside lounge, playground, and paved walking/jogging paths. Conveniently located close to highways, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Your perfect home in Jacksonville awaits! All information pertaining to the property is deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Information to be verified by the Buyer.
